{"tid":2058567,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"楊潤雄：教師參與罷課等於向學生示範以「違規方式」表達訴求　教育局會嚴肅跟進","createTime":"2020-06-10T09:19:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-10T09:56:19.000Z","uid":212626,"like":3,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"6e0b88c6bf08d5d86842696f9cfa3007040c0c2e","tid":2058567,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T09:19:46.000Z","msg":"教育局長楊潤雄去信全港中小學校長，指近日有團體發起反對港區國安法的網上聯署，故意誤導和煽動學生參與所謂「罷工罷課公投」，政府予以強烈譴責，批評有關活動是以學生的利益和前途作為籌碼，<span style=\"color: red;\">強調學校不應任由學生參加，更不應容許罷課，如果發現有學生組織或慫恿同學參加違法活動、罷課或校內政治活動，應該立即勸止，如屢勸不改，就要按校本訓育輔導和懲處機制處理</span>。<br />\n<br />\n楊潤雄又指，<span style=\"color: red;\">教師不可以放事假參與罷課，如果參與，將是疏忽職守</span>，將政治帶入校園，向學生示範以違規方式表達訴求，有違專業，校方應採取紀律行動，教育局亦會嚴肅跟進。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1305201&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1305201%26csid%3D261_341&d=TNVh%2FXBsTmD9bRjMILuVa6Ggm0NOSfkDZSs230CVm%2Fs%3D&h=fd47b7df\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1305201&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"ed4dc2a691ad0d426b07b868aaf7dfed72fbe7ef","tid":2058567,"uid":205162,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T09:20:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0225d1231c42bb6f13cc931dae0454ee52ee0423","tid":2058567,"uid":217450,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T09:20:40.000Z","msg":"一年咁多日病假，我隔日請請足兩個足我屌你老母支那楊"},{"pid":"7d87e2c2528c0fee1e074c6d06391ebe53716572","tid":2058567,"uid":212626,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T09:22:12.000Z","msg":"請假都唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid"